The paper deals with the design of space-time lattice codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also uses concepts from algebraic geometry (cs.GR) and computational complexity (cs.SD). The simulations and experiments involve numerical analysis (cs.NA) and machine learning (cs.LG).
